#8.title: Increase max_gas devnet limits
#8.message: Current devnet TPS is limited by max_gas set to 10500000, allowing 500 EVM transactions per block. We want to increse the TPS of the devnet by a factor of 2.

#32.title: Extend governance voting time to 7 days
#32.message: Current voting time is set to 2 days. This property allowed fast changes in the network when less nodes were participating. Now that we have achieved better decentralization, we want to set the voting time for 7 days to allow nodes to have more time to decide and participate in governance proposals.

#34.title: Enable IBC by allowing cosmos tokens
#34.message: Modify bank parameters to allow the send of cosmos tokens. This change will allow receiving transfers from other chains connected through IBC.
